member.returns:
200 OK if the product was successfully added to favourites;
401 Unauthorized if the user is not authenticated or the user ID is invalid;
409 Conflict if the product is already in the user's favourites;
500 Internal Server Error for unexpected server errors.

200 OK if the product was successfully removed from favourites;
401 Unauthorized if the user is not authenticated or the user ID is invalid;
404 Not Found if the product is not in the user's favourites;
500 Internal Server Error for unexpected server errors.

200 OK with the list of favourites if the user is authenticated;
401 Unauthorized if the user is not authenticated or the user ID is invalid;
500 Internal Server Error for unexpected server errors.

200 OK with the created order details if successful;
400 Bad Request if the user email is not found in the JWT token;
500 Internal Server Error for unexpected errors.
